results.abstract: Lyakhov and Ryumin dock Soyuz spacecraft with orbiting Salyut space station (S)
results.snippet: MOSCOW, Feb. 26 (AP)--Two Soviet astronauts docked their Soyuz capsule and boarded the space laboratory Salyut 6 today to begin a series of experiments in the lab, which has been orbiting the earth for nearly a year and a half.
